Line5.789BF: But I won’t ever shirk my duty in bringing Elias to justice. That is the part of Valtha I will never understand.
Line3.789BF: I understand why she saw a future in Lilith. The Mother of Sanctuary isn’t so different from the witches of Hawezar.
Line1.789BF: Valtha forged me into the witch I am. I struggle with her death...
